- Golden Gate Global. Advantages of the EB-5 Visa for International Students (F-1 Visa Holders). [https://www.3gfund.com/eb-5-visa-for-international-students/](https://www.3gfund.com/eb-5-visa-for-international-students/)
- EB5 United. EB-5 Visa Investment Cost & Regional Center Fee for 2025. [https://www.eb5united.com/eb5-visa/cost/](https://www.eb5united.com/eb5-visa/cost/)
- EB5 United. EB-5 Set Asides. [https://www.eb5united.com/eb5-visa/set-asides/](https://www.eb5united.com/eb5-visa/set-asides/)
- USCIS. Approved EB-5 Immigrant Investor Regional Centers. [https://www.uscis.gov/working-in-the-united-states/permanent-workers/employment-based-immigration-fifth-preference-eb-5/eb-5-immigrant-investor-regional-centers/approved-eb-5-immigrant-investor-regional-centers](https://www.uscis.gov/working-in-the-united-states/permanent-workers/employment-based-immigration-fifth-preference-eb-5/eb-5-immigrant-investor-regional-centers/approved-eb-5-immigrant-investor-regional-centers)
- Forbes. Why 2025 Is A Rare Opportunity For The EB-5 Regional Investor Program. [https://www.forbes.com/sites/andyjsemotiuk/2025/12/18/why-2025-is-a-rare-opportunity-for-the-eb-5-regional-investor-program/](https://www.forbes.com/sites/andyjsemotiuk/2025/12/18/why-2025-is-a-rare-opportunity-for-the-eb-5-regional-investor-program/)
- EB5 Visa Investments. What EB-5 Investors Want in a Regional Center. [https://eb5visainvestments.com/2024/09/10/is-eb-5-worth-it-an-in-depth-look/](https://eb5visainvestments.com/2024/09/10/is-eb-5-worth-it-an-in-depth-look/)
## Frequently Asked Questions

### How does concurrent filing benefit F-1 students applying for the EB-5 program?

Concurrent filing allows F-1 students to submit their I-485 adjustment of status petition simultaneously with their I-526E petition. This grants authorized stay during adjudication and eligibility for an employment authorization document (EAD) and Advance Parole (AP) travel document. Students receive the interim benefits of having a green card before actually getting the green card. These benefits allow students to work for any employer, travel internationally without restrictions, and avoid F-1 visa limitations such as on-campus work restrictions and the competitive <a href="/tools/opt-calculator">OPT program</a>. For a detailed walkthrough of the F-1 to EB-5 journey, see our <a href="/research/f1-students/f1-to-eb5-green-card">comprehensive 2026 guide</a>.

### What are the key benefits of the EB-5 visa program for F-1 students beyond permanent residency?

The EB-5 visa offers significant employer, education and travel benefits. EB-5 holders can work and start businesses freely, access in-state tuition rates, qualify for federal financial aid and scholarships and enjoy broader admission and internship opportunities. They also gain the ability to travel internationally without the constraints of temporary visas which substantially lowers overall education costs and increases flexibility during their studies. Use our <a href="/tools/tuition-calculator">Tuition Savings Calculator</a> to estimate the potential education cost savings of obtaining a green card.

- The Modi Law Firm. Understanding the Financial Requirements for an EB-5 Visa. [https://www.themodilawfirm.com/research/2025/october/understanding-the-financial-requirements-for-an-/](https://www.themodilawfirm.com/research/2025/october/understanding-the-financial-requirements-for-an-/)
- Golden Gate Global. Navigating the I-485 Adjustment of Status for EB-5 Investors Residing in the U.S.. [https://www.3gfund.com/eb-5-visa-concurrent-filing/](https://www.3gfund.com/eb-5-visa-concurrent-filing/)

---

